Chef#account_activation

<%= @greeting %>

    Thanks for requesting to re-activate your Recipe-Share account.
    Here's the activation link to confirm your request.

<%= "#{Rails.application.credentials.server[Rails.env.to_sym]}/reactivate?token=#{@chef.activation_digest}&email=#{@chef.e_mail.split("@").join("%40")}" %>

    Once you confirm you want to re-activate your account, we'll reset your password and send a follow up e-mail.
    Welcome back!
    Recipe-Share Admin"